but I have to talk to you about Pilgrim.

108
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,276
<i>Hello?</i>

109
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:23,151
Yeah, I'm here.

110
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:26,357
<i>I've never seen an animal
with these injuries still breathing.</i>

111
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:28,954
