125
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:17,514
Nothing.
He's just going off duty.

126
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:23,512
Well! That's important information, huh?

127
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,352
Christ.

128
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:27,556
Doctors, huh?

129
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:36,077
I'm gonna get to know all
the nurses' names.

130
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:44,716
