195
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:11,318
Everything.
Medical publications as well.

196
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:14,039
Veterinarian journals. And tell them
it's me, and I want it now.

197
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:17,550
- Hold on, hold on. Gottschalk.
- I'll call him back.

198
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:19,750
